<span class="label">News</span>
<h2>Epigenomics Now</h2>
<h6 class="subheader"></h6>
</div>
<hr class="dotted" />
<div id="articleFullText" class="col1 floatLeft firstCol">
<span class="byline">
By Don Monroe
<br/>
Communications of the ACM,
January 2024,
Vol. 67 No. 1, Pages 11-13<br/>
10.1145/3631934<br/>
<a href="#comments">Comments</a>
</span>
